data.description: If you're looking for a peaceful and serene escape, this is the perfect place for you! Situated on just under 5 acres of land, this home offers breathtaking views from every corner. Enjoy your morning cup of coffee out in the fresh air while taking in the natural beauty that surrounds you. You'll have ample space to explore with marketable timber as well as plenty of room to store any vehicles or toys in the large two-car garage with shop area. Whether you're looking to move right in or make it a weekend getaway, don't miss out on this gorgeous location!
